data.description: Welcome to your waterfront oasis on Wolf Bay in Orange Beach, Alabama! This stunning home offers a rare opportunity to indulge in the serene beauty of coastal living while enjoying the comforts of a luxurious residence. Situated on a prime lot, this property boasts breathtaking panoramic views of Wolf Bay, where the calm waters meet the horizon. The picturesque sunsets will leave you awe-inspired each evening as you relax on your large private deck or take a dip in the refreshing waters of your own backyard. Step inside the main level to an open concept floor plan that seamlessly blends the indoor and outdoor spaces, creating a seamless flow that maximizes the bay views from every angle. Expansive windows flood the living spaces with natural light, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The large enclosed sunroom is the perfect place to hang out, and includes a portable AC unit to make sure you stay cool in the summer! The master suite is off to the side, with sunroom access, a large walk-in closet, and handicap-accessible shower. The open kitchen is a dream, equipped with a gas stovetop, brand new double ovens, built in ice-maker, and refrigerator, all stainless! The 13x8 pantry is worth mentioning, providing all the space you could need for storage! Gather around the elegant dining area for memorable meals with family and friends, or step outside to the sunroom or deck for al fresco dining amidst the gentle bay breeze. Follow the winding spiral staircase to the crow's nest to watch for dolphins and passing boats. Take the stairs or private elevator to the ground floor and discover an entire separate living area, bedroom, bathroom, and laundry room! This home has it all with space, views, privacy, and comfort!
